text: Phwk cea nan pen prachachati thi di ying sung thuk hı xubati khun sahrab mnusʹychati doythi phwk cea chı hı ptibati sing thi chxb læa ham mi hı ptibati sing thi mi chxb læa sraththa tx xallxhˌ læa thahakwa brrda phu thi di rab khamphir sraththa kan læw nænxn man k penkar di kæ phwk khea swn hnung cak phwk khea nan mi brrda phu thi sraththa læa swn mak khxng phwk khea nan pen phu lameid
